## 📝 Persona 3: Scorer (Tablet/Web)

### Flow: Live Digital Scoring
1.  **Game Setup**: Selects Game. Confirms Lineups (Drag & Drop players to positions).
2.  **Play Loop**:
    -   Pitcher throws -> Scorer taps "Ball" or "Strike" or "Hit".
    -   If "Hit" -> Selects type (Line Drive) -> Location (Left Field).
    -   System asks: "Runner on 1st advanced?" -> Scorer taps "2nd Base".
3.  **End of Inning**: System auto-calculates runs/hits. Prompts "Switch Sides".
4.  **Game Over**: Clicks "Finalize Game". PDF generated.

### 🖼️ Wireframe: Scoring Interface (Tablet Landscape)

```text
+---------------------------------------------------------------+
| TIN VS BOS | INNING: ▲ 3 | OUTS: ● ○ | COUNT: 1-2 | [MENU]    |
