|         [CF]                  |  #12 J. Doe (Avg .320)        |
|     [LF]    [RF]              |                               |
|                               |  ACTION BUTTONS               |
|      [SS] [2B]                |  +-------+ +-------+ +-----+  |
|    [3B]      [1B]             |  | STRIKE| | BALL  | | FOUL|  |
|                               |  +-------+ +-------+ +-----+  |
|         [P]                   |                               |
|                               |  +-------+ +-------+ +-----+  |
|         [C]                   |  |  HIT  | |  OUT  | | RUN |  |
|                               |  +-------+ +-------+ +-----+  |
|                               |                               |
|  LOG:                         |  LAST PLAY:                   |
|  - Strike (Looking)           |  Ground out to SS (6-3)       |
|  - Ball (Low)                 |                               |
+---------------------------------------------------------------+
```

## 🗺️ Navigation Map (Sitemap)

-   **Public**: Landing Page, Login, Password Reset.
-   **Admin Portal**:
    -   Dashboard (KPIs)
    -   Leagues (CRUD)
    -   Users (Ampayers list, approval)
    -   Settings (Pricing, Rules)
-   **App**:
    -   Home (Feed)
    -   Schedule (Calendar)
    -   Profile (Stats, Earnings)
